page.title: 20THIS PROJECT
page.content: This work has been compiled by members of the SIXTH FORM of Princes Risborough County Secondary School. The courses that they follow at School are vocationally based with hire for general studies around the main courses. Two periods a week are given over to humanities and it has been during this time in the summer term 1985,that the work has been done. There were only five pupils in the group, aided by one member of staff. They all thoroughly enjoyed looking at their area in more detail and compiling the data. They were also pleased with the idea that their work would be recorded for posterity.
